# Error Handling (Template)

Define how this repo represents, logs, and surfaces errors.

Goal: predictable failures, actionable logs, and safe user-facing messages.

---

## Principles

- Prefer explicit error types/codes over free-form strings.
- Do not leak secrets or internal stack traces to untrusted clients.
- Log errors with enough context to debug, but avoid PII unless required.
- Make retry behaviour explicit (which errors are retriable, which are not).

